data.description: Location Location Location!  Neatly tucked away in one of Orlando's most convenient locations, this beautiful home is literally minutes from everything.  Just a short drive to Downtown Orlando, the 408, I4, the International Airport and all the Theme Parks, and a short drive to either one of Central Florida's coasts, you will never run out of things to do in the amazing location.  The curved driveway welcomes you into your oversized garage, with more than enough space for two cars and storage.  The open layout of the home ensures a smooth flow, where everyone will be greeted by loads of natural light bouncing all throughout your beautiful home.  Large bedrooms give everyone more than enough space, and the private, secluded yard with fruit producing trees make this abode the perfect paradise to call your next home!  AC is less than a year old, and the water softener is also less than a year old as well!  Don't wait!
